  "texts": [
    "For example, a rat trained to associate pressing a lever to get the reward.",
    "No individual cell has both experiences -the skin cells of the paws experience the lever, the cells in the gut get a metabolic reward.",
    "This associative memory belongs to the \"rat\" -the collective, and to none of the cells individually.",
    "Could having such memories actually help create the organism in a real sense?",
    "The body houses and maintains them, but perhaps they in turn make the virtual governor [188,189] that we call the cognitive Self more real?"
  ],
